2a=hole diameter=103±0.25 mils; 
&agr;=hole offset angle=60°; 
dx=hole spacing=123.5±0.5 mils; 
dy=vertical hole spacing=dx sin &agr;=107.0±0.5 mils; 
D=plate thickness=250±0.5 mils; 
L=dielectric thickness=36±0.25 mils; and 
&egr;r=dielectric constant=3.827 (fused silica at 95 GHz).
